<h2 style="text-align: center;" data-start="208" data-end="234">Advice on family visit</h2>
<p data-start="236" data-end="253"><strong data-start="236" data-end="253">Accommodation</strong></p>
<ul data-start="254" data-end="345">
<li data-start="254" data-end="290">
<p data-start="256" data-end="290">{Kings|King’s} Hotel on George Street</p>
</li>
<li data-start="291" data-end="345">
<p data-start="293" data-end="345">cost of family room per night: {125|one hundred (and) twenty-five}<br data-start="225" data-end="228"> (approx.)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="347" data-end="368"><strong data-start="347" data-end="368">Recommended trips</strong></p>
<ul data-start="369" data-end="473">
<li data-start="369" data-end="435">
<p data-start="371" data-end="435">a {walking} tour of the city centre (starts in Carlton Square)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="436" data-end="473">
<p data-start="438" data-end="473">a trip by {boat} to the old fort</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="475" data-end="493"><strong data-start="475" data-end="493">Science Museum</strong></p>
<ul data-start="494" data-end="581">
<li data-start="494" data-end="526">
<p data-start="496" data-end="526">best day to visit: {Tuesday}</p>
</li>
<li data-start="527" data-end="581">
<p data-start="529" data-end="581">see the exhibition about {space}, which opens soon</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="583" data-end="591"><strong data-start="583" data-end="591">Food</strong></p>
<ul data-start="592" data-end="686">
<li data-start="592" data-end="686">
<p data-start="594" data-end="686">Clacton Market:<br data-start="609" data-end="612">– good for {vegetarian} food<br data-start="639" data-end="642">– need to have lunch before {2.30|two thirty} p.m.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="688" data-end="707"><strong data-start="688" data-end="707">Theatre tickets</strong></p>
<ul data-start="708" data-end="771">
<li data-start="708" data-end="771">
<p data-start="710" data-end="771">save up to {75|seventy-five} % on ticket prices at bargaintickets.com</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="773" data-end="792"><strong data-start="773" data-end="792">Free activities</strong></p>
<ul data-start="793" data-end="899" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-start="793" data-end="899" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="795" data-end="899" data-is-last-node="">Blakewell Gardens:<br data-start="813" data-end="816">– Roots Music Festival<br data-start="840" data-end="843">– climb Telegraph Hill to see a view of the {port}</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
